Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["standard deviation",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " is just the square root of the variance, representing the spread of the \
data around the mean. But also, within 2 standard deviation your data (for \
gaussian statistics) should be found as bellow (68.2%)"
}], "Item",
