Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Diagnostic analysis: Covariance and correlation statistics.", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777033496043618*^9, 3.777033497422864*^9}, {
  3.8112489744782324`*^9, 
  3.811248979360964*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"6707a264-cd06-4d67-8a3f-\
7eb7ff58d25b"],

Cell["\<\
\[Bullet]Used for discovery, or to determine why something happened
\[Bullet]Most commonly used technique: correlation, but to determine why \
something happened requires the use of causal measurements which allows the \
identification of the relationship of cause-effect.    \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.88486356936574*^9, 3.88486358870172*^9}, {
  3.884949481983591*^9, 3.884949586070488*^9}, {3.907146035578706*^9, 
  3.9071460951144257`*^9}},
 Background->RGBColor[
  0.87, 0.94, 1],ExpressionUUID->"a42ecd5f-6c6a-4dc1-880d-bbbeb30e2db5"],

Cell["\<\
Covariance is the multivariate extension of variance [Wolfram], used to \
analyse dispersion in a singe variable.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777097248559313*^9, 3.777097251615328*^9}, {
   3.777097377320321*^9, 3.777097381767583*^9}, {3.8446638882039948`*^9, 
   3.844663904423789*^9}, 
   3.884863591470295*^9},ExpressionUUID->"53c50a88-7543-427d-ae4d-\
5706641bb86b"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"[", 
   ButtonBox["Wikipedia",
    BaseStyle->"Hyperlink",
    ButtonData->{
      URL["https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covariance_and_correlation"], None},
    ButtonNote->"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Covariance_and_correlation"], 
   "]"}], ":"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777096102874558*^9, 3.777096108369104*^9}, 
   3.777096516011091*^9, 3.777097258086512*^9, {3.777097354490753*^9, 
   3.7770973629158916`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"26e51721-536b-48e9-af75-\
475511beca21"],

Cell["\<\
In probability theory and statistics, the mathematical concepts of covariance \
and correlation are very similar. Both describe the degree to which two \
random variables or sets of random variables tend to deviate from their \
expected values in similar ways.

However,\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.777096109896418*^9, 3.777096135506915*^9}, {
  3.777096205845714*^9, 3.777096230587037*^9}, {3.7770962700622396`*^9, 
  3.777096344789701*^9}, {3.777096388127881*^9, 3.777096412125512*^9}, {
  3.777096630173066*^9, 3.777096646310655*^9}, {3.777096781749197*^9, 
  3.777096805279524*^9}, {3.777097323735771*^9, 3.7770973298915386`*^9}, {
  3.777097387369553*^9, 3.777097388863107*^9}, {3.780145827198989*^9, 
  3.780145831230743*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"9437fe11-b3e4-4279-b949-\
29d821fd7ad2"],

