  "SlideShowHeader",ExpressionUUID->"57173d25-46a6-45a8-bbea-1e5b00ab2937"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "Predictive ",
 StyleBox["analytics",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->True}],
 StyleBox[" (",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->False}],
 StyleBox["what I would call model-free prediction", "Section",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->True}],
 StyleBox[")",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->False}]
}], "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811249293639594*^9, 3.811249296152336*^9}, {
  3.884949617337522*^9, 
  3.884949633702792*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"b42d49d2-e90b-4de6-8d63-\
923d1f91a1ce"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["Here, we mean a machine learning method for example, where the \
equations describing the system are not necessarily known, or only partially \
known",
  FontWeight->"Bold",
  FontVariations->{"Underline"->True}],
 ". The model however predicts the system.  "
}], "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811249315452825*^9, 3.811249328222793*^9}, {
  3.90715970554352*^9, 
  3.907159709446299*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c1466388-af7b-4456-90e2-\
f341ff6c883b"],

Cell["\<\
Obtain insight from hindsight as we identify patterns from existing data\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811249315452825*^9, 3.811249328222793*^9}, 
   3.90715970554352*^9},ExpressionUUID->"0ce16654-9bf1-4677-a636-\
507e1abda101"],

Cell["\<\
Then use such insights to predict the future : foresight. The hidden patterns \
unveiled by the process makes it possible to make predictions.\
\>", "Item",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.811249315452825*^9, 3.8112493277390943`*^9}, {
  3.8132418777961884`*^9, 3.813241931164648*^9}, {3.907159704143678*^9, 
  3.907159712467769*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"de8fe948-0bb7-48ef-9307-\
2cb901ef5bf9"],

